    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If the double quotes only exist at the beginning and the end, a simple code as this would work perfectly:</p>\n\n<p><code>string = string.replace(\"\\\"\", \"\");</code></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 6974471,
      "reputation" : 29,
      "user_id" : 5349643,
      "user_type" : "unregistered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/5a3cd3abebb033b572276109c4582999?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
