    "question_id" : 2608665,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<pre><code>Matcher m = Pattern.compile(\"^\\\"(.*)\\\"$\").matcher(value);\nString strUnquoted = value;\nif (m.find()) {\n    strUnquoted = m.group(1);\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
